OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNew Brit School North in   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FBradford gets go-ahead     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Plans to base a northern version of    
OL,6, London's renowned Brit School in       
OL,7, Bradford have been given the go-ahead  
OL,8, by the government.                     
OL,10,FThe new Brit School North will be free 
OL,11,Fto attend for 500 pupils aged 16 to 19.
OL,13,FIt will offer courses in dance, music  
OL,14,Fand theatre.                           
OL,16,FThe original Brit School in Croydon,   
OL,17,Fsouth London, opened its doors in 1991 
OL,18,Fand has helped launch the careers of   
OL,19,Fstars including including Adele, Amy   
OL,20,FWinehouse, Tom Holland and Jessie J.   
